    },
    {
      "type": "image_picker",
      "id": "arrow_1_img",
      "label": "Arrow Icon Asset 1"
    },
    {
      "type": "image_picker",
      "id": "arrow_2_img",
      "label": "Arrow Icon Asset 2"
    },
    {
      "type": "header",
      "content": "Arrow 1 Precision X & Y Coordinates"
    },
    {
      "type": "range",
      "id": "arrow_1_x",
      "min": 0,
      "max": 100,
      "step": 1,
      "unit": "%",
      "label": "Arrow 1 Horizontal Coordinate (Left)",
      "default": 42
    },
    {
      "type": "range",
      "id": "arrow_1_y",
      "min": 0,
      "max": 100,
      "step": 1,
      "unit": "%",
      "label": "Arrow 1 Vertical Coordinate (Top)",
      "default": 18
    },
    {
      "type": "range",
      "id": "arrow_1_w",
      "min": 20,
      "max": 120,
      "step": 2,
      "unit": "px",
      "label": "Arrow 1 Structural Sizing Scale Width",
      "default": 36
    },
    {
      "type": "header",
      "content": "Arrow 2 Precision X & Y Coordinates"
    },
    {
      "type": "range",
      "id": "arrow_2_x",
      "min": 0,
      "max": 100,
      "step": 1,
      "unit": "%",
      "label": "Arrow 2 Horizontal Coordinate (Left)",
      "default": 24
    },
    {
      "type": "range",
      "id": "arrow_2_y",
      "min": 0,
      "max": 100,
      "step": 1,
      "unit": "%",
      "label": "Arrow 2 Vertical Coordinate (Top)",
      "default": 46
    },
    {
      "type": "range",
      "id": "arrow_2_w",
      "min": 20,
      "max": 120,
      "step": 2,
      "unit": "px",
      "label": "Arrow 2 Structural Sizing Scale Width",
      "default": 36
    },
    {
      "type": "header",
      "content": "Text Element Content Libraries"
    },
    {
      "type": "richtext",
      "id": "top_right_para",
      "label": "Top Right Description text",
      "default": "<p>Real foods contain over 26000 distinct bio-active compounds, these compounds play critical roles in modulating inflammation, supporting gut microbiome and preventing chronic disease</p>"
    },
    {
      "type": "richtext",
      "id": "bottom_left_para",
      "label": "Bottom Left Description text",
      "default": "<p>Whole food also bring in the benefits of co-factors also called \"The Entourage Effect\" bringing the synergistic benefit of real food</p>"
    },
    {
      "type": "richtext",
      "id": "right_heading",
      "label": "Right Side Main Bold Heading",
      "default": "<p>Our Formulations have human-grade, bioavailable ingredients best suited to your pet's digestive system.</p>"
    },
    {
      "type": "richtext",
      "id": "center_baseline_para",
      "label": "Center Aligned Baseline Paragraph text",
      "default": "<p>Since all nutrients are not equal, we source specific amino acid profiles to build muscle and immunity, and strictly use anti-inflammatory fats that fight disease rather than fuel it.</p>"
    },
    {
      "type": "header",
      "content": "Global Design Theme Palette Overrides"
    },
    {
      "type": "color",
      "id": "text_color_dark",
      "label": "Primary Base Dark Typography Color",
      "default": "#1a1a1a"
    },
    {
      "type": "color",
      "id": "text_color_accent",
      "label": "Brand Focal Accent Highlight Color",
      "default": "#d93829"
    }
  ],
  "presets": [
    {
      "name": "Solution Matrix Blocks"
    }
  ]
